Created 1.11.1995 by renaming the parish of Langley. See also 
    Table 2, note (m).

Abolished 1.4.1974 to become an unparished area. See also Table 
    2, note (a).

Unparished area which until 1.4.1974 formed the parish of Chester-le-Street. See also Table 2, note 
    (m).

Unparished area which until 1.4.1974 formed the parishes of Consett 
    and Stanley. See also Table 2, notes (i) and (m).

Abolished 1.4.1974 and added to the Sunderland unparished area. See also Table 
    2, notes (a), (c), (f), (g) and (k).

Created 1.4.1986 out of the parishes of Framwellgate Moor, 
    Kimblesworth and Plawsworth. See also Table 2, note (l).

Abolished 1.4.1985 and added to the parish of Bournmoor. See 
    also Table 2, note (a).

Renamed 1.11.1995 to create the parish of Burnhope. See also Table 2, note 
    (m).

Created 1.4.1974 out of the parish of Harraton. See also Table 
    2, note (m).

Abolished 1.4.1986 and added to the parish of 
    Kimblesworth & Plawsworth. See also Table 2, notes (a) and (b).

Abolished 1.4.1985 and added to the parish of Bournmoor. See 
    also Table 2, notes (a) and (k).

Abolished 1.4.1974 and added to the Sunderland unparished area. See also Table 
    2, notes (a), (e), (f) and (k).
